# ── Input data and generated results ─────────────────────────────────────
# This repository ships code only. Input data are downloaded by the scripts
# in each module, and sample-specific network matrices are regenerated from
# them. The patterns below keep large data and intermediate results out of
# version control.
*.csv
*.tsv
*.rds
*.RDS
*.rda
*.h5
*.gz
*.bz2
*.zip
*.tar
*.xlsx
*.xls

# figures / reports produced by the plotting scripts
*.pdf
*.tif
*.tiff
*.png
*.jpg
*.svg

# generated output directories
1Matrix/
1result/
results/
